# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  GoTweaks Lite — repository ignore rules
#  Keeps regenerable build output, secrets, and local agent state
#  out of the repo. Native dependency DLLs live in the project
#  *source* folders (e.g. XboxGamingBarHelper/*.dll) and ARE tracked.
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── .NET / MSBuild build output ─────────────────────────────────
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/

# ── MSIX / packaging output ─────────────────────────────────────
**/AppPackages/
**/BundleArtifacts/
*.appx
*.appxbundle
*.appxupload
*.msix
*.msixbundle
*.msixupload
_pkginfo.txt

# ── Visual Studio / IDE ─────────────────────────────────────────
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.VC.db
*.VC.opendb
*.dtbcache.json

# ── NuGet restore folder (regenerated by `restore`) ─────────────
packages/
*.nupkg
.nuget/

# ── Signing keys & certs — NEVER commit a private key ───────────
#  The dev/self-signed cert is shipped as a GitHub Release asset
#  (alongside the installer), not committed to the source tree.
*.pfx
*.p12
*.snk
*.cer

# ── Logs / local runtime artifacts ──────────────────────────────
*.log
helper_*.log
widget_*.log
helper_heartbeat.json

# ── Claude / AI assistant — nothing AI-related goes in the repo ─
#  Per-user memory under ~/.claude lives OUTSIDE this tree and is
#  never committed. These rules cover the in-tree AI files too:
#  CLAUDE.md (portable project notes) and any local agent state.
.claude/
CLAUDE.md
**/CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
**/AGENTS.md

# ── Release staging produced by Build-Release.ps1 ───────────────
dist/

# ── OS cruft ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
